data.description: This charming two bedroom two story home is a must see. Upstairs Primary bedroom and loft. The primary bedroom features two separate showers and two walk-in closets. An oversized family room for those special family gatherings. The kitchen features ceramic tile and a white refrigerator which will remain with the house, it has a wrap around bar and an eat-in breakfast nook. Laundry room is located just off the kitchen which also includes under the stair storage along with storage above a pair of full size washer and dryer. The owner is willing to leave the washer and dryer for the new owners. The second bedroom is on the first floor next to the bathroom which is great for a guest. This property sits in a quiet residential area not far from restaurants & shopping. It offers a rear two car garage through a residential alleyway.  Don't miss out on this great opportunity.
